       STAGE 1 — BEGINNER
       ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
    <div id="beginner" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-10);">
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="border-color:#16a34a;">🌱 Stage 1 — Complete Beginner</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted); font-size:var(--text-sm); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">You're new to UPSC or just decided to prepare. Understand the exam first, then build a strong foundation.</p>

      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-5); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Week 1 — Know the Exam</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Understand the 3-stage structure (Prelims → Mains → Interview), marking scheme, and syllabus. Read the <a href="/resources/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Resources page</a> for booklist and strategy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Week 2 — Start Polity</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Begin with <a href="/subjects/polity/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Polity</a> — it's the most structured subject. Read Preamble, Fundamental Rights, and DPSPs to build momentum.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Week 3 — Add Economy &amp; Geography</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Start <a href="/subjects/economy/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Economy</a> (overview + banking) and <a href="/subjects/geography/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Geography</a> (physical geography). One topic per day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Week 4 — Build the Daily Habit</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Start 30 min/day current affairs on <a href="https://ujiyari.com/daily/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Ujiyari.com</a>. This habit will carry you through the entire preparation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

