    {# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       STAGE 4 — REVISION MODE
       ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
    <div id="revision" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-10);">
      <h2 class="section-heading" style="border-color:#7c3aed;">🔄 Stage 4 — Revision Mode</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted); font-size:var(--text-sm); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">Exam is close. No new topics — only revise, practise, and consolidate what you already know.</p>

      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-5); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Revise Using Bookmarks</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Open your <a href="/tracker/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">bookmarked topics</a> and re-read the key sections. Focus on tables, mnemonics, and fact sheets you built.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">PYQs as Flashcards</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Go through <a href="/pyq/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">PYQ trends</a> by subject. Can you answer each theme confidently? If not, that topic needs one more pass.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Vocab &amp; Terms Sprint</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Final pass through <a href="/resources/vocab-builder/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Vocab Builder</a> and <a href="/resources/key-terms/" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">Key Terms</a>. These small details make the difference on exam day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-card">
          <h4 class="strategy-card__title">Current Affairs Consolidation</h4>
          <p class="strategy-card__text">Read <a href="https://ujiyari.com/monthly/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--color-brand); font-weight:600;">monthly digests</a> for the last 12 months. In the final week, focus only on the last 6 months.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

